{"tid":1367214,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【香港隻揪】勁揪體文宣原檔下載 (代貼)","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:17:16.000Z","uid":267678,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"894f65a8cb6d0343cb9be056bb2efc98cb0f91fd","tid":1367214,"uid":267678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"代勁揪體創作人Kit Man貼上嚟，有幾款A3圖俾大家，印出嚟派街坊又得，貼連儂牆又得，佢仲想同大家講︰<br />\n只要大家唔放棄，我都唔會放棄⋯⋯ 香港人加油 T __ T<br />\n<br />\n【727和理優・不入村不開波・對家出手會還拖】<br />\n當惡勢力動用特權，法律，暴力，黑社會，企圖要我哋低頭嘅時候，作為有種嘅香港人，唔好意思，我哋真係唔習慣跪。<br />\n重申五大訴求<br />\n#立即實行雙普選<br />\n#撤回逃犯條例<br />\n#撤回暴動定性<br />\n#追究警隊濫暴<br />\n#釋放抗爭者<br />\n<br />\nA3/ 300 dpi 印刷級海報 ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/727_Poster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F727_Poster&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=9695f45c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/727_Poster</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fwatmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fwatmK.jpg&h=19d9b686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【罷工罷上腦，非商用任用】中意行街街嘅你，你咪成日為咗無嘢擋太陽 / 無嘢撥涼而煩惱呢？？？星期五，我哋送禮勤部隊又到送百萬當係碎銀嘅時間啦！！！（起乳豬歌⋯⋯）<br />\n<br />\nPDF FILE - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/HK_Messages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHK_Messages&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=5e621500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HK_Messages</a> （非商用任用）<br />\n<br />\n呢度有 8 款 A3 SIZE （其實係 AI 可以放到隧道口 BILLBOARD 咁大）嘅標語，有部份係早前放過出嚟，諗住比大家加圖加色乜乜乜。點知無人二創，唯有我哋自己二創返啦⋯ 後面兩個新款係同媽媽谷傾過，有關黑道同家教嘅標語，希望家長都會啱用。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係印刷商又好想回饋社會嘅，請隨便攞去印呀派呀乜乜乜，話說之前喺 SOGO 有得派果批，其實我都好想要，但都搵唔到，嗚哇⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n長期抗爭，我哋知道大家會攰，希望呢少少禮物可以為你哋打下氣！一路咁落去，係要你撐下我，我又撐下你咁，先有力一齊繼續走下去！<br />\n香港人加油！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpVnjto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpVnjto.png&h=9ef6a7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esjvtmH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesjvtmH.png&h=5b67cb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOUfEtk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOUfEtk.png&h=ce620231&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLDzU1G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLDzU1G.png&h=dca8fc40&s={SIZE}\" />   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oqyq8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oqyq8k.png&h=0c1a8703&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RD3PJU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRD3PJU1.png&h=7041b1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzU3OmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzU3OmK.png&h=d47bc22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3e25he2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3e25he2.png&h=5e4b2f4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c2fd73bb55f65408b8eca47f141fbed9e47beb8","tid":1367214,"uid":260903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借個位推一推，人人都可以整文宣：<br />\n<br />\n【教學】自己文宣自己整，自己香港自己救：唔駛Ps/Ai，免費整圖app Canva<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30d2f78776ba89a8d852fd967342c10c651500e6","tid":1367214,"uid":267678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c2fd73bb55f65408b8eca47f141fbed9e47beb8","tid":1367214,"uid":260903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借個位推一推